    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="教你制作炫酷的html烟花特效"><a href="#教你制作炫酷的html烟花特效" class="headerlink" title="教你制作炫酷的html烟花特效"></a>教你制作炫酷的html烟花特效</h1><p>​        想在html中做出烟花特效吗？</p><p>​        想让自己的网页更加出色吗？</p><p>​        你需要”他“！</p><h2 id="让我们开始吧！"><a href="#让我们开始吧！" class="headerlink" title="让我们开始吧！"></a>让我们开始吧！</h2><ul><li><p>首先，在桌面上新建一个文本文档，文档名随意。</p></li><li><p>然后，进入文档编辑，把下列代码复制进去。</p></li><li><pre><code class="html"><span class="meta">&lt;!doctype <span class="meta-keyword">html</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"en"</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span>  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>SUPER FIREWORKS!<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span>  <span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="meta-keyword">html</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"en"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span>    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>&gt;</span>    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>Fireworks<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"text/css"</span>&gt;</span>    body{<span class="css">      <span class="selector-tag">background</span>:<span class="selector-id">#000</span>;</span><span class="css">      <span class="selector-tag">margin</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:0</span>;</span><span class="css">      <span class="selector-tag">width</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:100</span>%;</span><span class="css">      <span class="selector-tag">overflow</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hidden</span>;</span>    }    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">canvas</span>&gt;</span>#FFFFFF<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">canvas</span>&gt;</span>    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="actionscript">        alert(<span class="string">"BE READY TO BE SUPRISED~"</span>);</span><span class="actionscript">        <span class="keyword">var</span> t = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><span class="javascript">        <span class="keyword">var</span> c = <span class="built_in">document</span>.querySelector(<span class="string">"canvas"</span>);     </span><span class="actionscript">        <span class="keyword">var</span> $ = c.getContext(<span class="string">'2d'</span>);</span><span class="javascript">        c.width = <span class="built_in">window</span>.innerWidth;</span><span class="javascript">        c.height = <span class="built_in">window</span>.innerHeight;</span><span class="javascript">        $.fillStyle = <span class="string">'hsla(0,0%,0%,1)'</span>;</span><span class="javascript">        <span class="built_in">window</span>.addEventListener(<span class="string">'resize'</span>, <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>) </span>{</span><span class="javascript">          c.width = <span class="built_in">window</span>.innerWidth;</span><span class="javascript">          c.height = <span class="built_in">window</span>.innerHeight;</span><span class="actionscript">        }, <span class="literal">false</span>);</span><span class="actionscript">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">draw</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>{</span><span class="javascript">          $.globalCompositeOperation = <span class="string">'source-over'</span>;</span><span class="javascript">          $.fillStyle = <span class="string">'hsla(0,0%,0%,.1)'</span>;</span><span class="javascript">          $.fillRect(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, c.width, c.height);</span><span class="actionscript">          <span class="keyword">var</span> foo, i, j, r;</span><span class="javascript">          foo = <span class="built_in">Math</span>.sin(t) * <span class="number">2</span> * <span class="built_in">Math</span>.PI;</span>          for (i=0; i&lt;400; i++) {<span class="javascript">            r = <span class="number">400</span> * <span class="built_in">Math</span>.sin(i * foo);</span><span class="javascript">            $.globalCompositeOperation = <span class="string">''</span>;</span><span class="javascript">            $.fillStyle = <span class="string">'hsla('</span> + i + <span class="number">12</span> + <span class="string">',100%, 60%,1)'</span>;</span><span class="javascript">            $.beginPath();</span><span class="javascript">            $.arc(<span class="built_in">Math</span>.sin(i) * r + (c.width / <span class="number">2</span>), </span><span class="javascript">                  <span class="built_in">Math</span>.cos(i) * r + (c.height / <span class="number">2</span>), </span><span class="javascript">                  <span class="number">1.5</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="built_in">Math</span>.PI * <span class="number">2</span>);</span><span class="javascript">            $.fill();</span>          }<span class="actionscript">          <span class="comment">//this controls the effect</span></span><span class="actionscript">          <span class="comment">//      ↓↓↓</span></span>          t += 0.000005;<span class="javascript">          <span class="keyword">return</span> t %= <span class="number">2</span> * <span class="built_in">Math</span>.PI;<span class="comment">//MATH.PI：π</span></span>        };<span class="actionscript">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">run</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>{</span><span class="javascript">          <span class="built_in">window</span>.requestAnimationFrame(run);</span>          draw();        }        run();    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></code></pre></li><li><p>退出保存，文件后缀改为  <strong>.html</strong></p></li><li><p>打开欣赏美妙的烟花吧</p><h3 id="PS：有点催眠，可拿去当屏保【滑稽】"><a href="#PS：有点催眠，可拿去当屏保【滑稽】" class="headerlink" title="PS：有点催眠，可拿去当屏保【滑稽】"></a>PS：有点催眠，可拿去当屏保【滑稽】</h3></li></ul>]]></content>
    
